UKSEDS Rocketry Competition
This year StrathSEDS will take part in the first UK SEDS run national rocketry championship

UMAAPS

This year StrathSEDS will take part in the first UK SEDS run national rocketry championship. The rocket will reach an altitude of 1Km and must carry a scientific payload of some description.
Points in the competition will be scored for the fastest time to 1km as well as for the originality and scientific merit of the payload, more information on the competition can be found on the UKSEDS Website.

The rocket is currently under development and further updates will be available here in the near future.
